Class DelegatingServiceProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.core.domain.DelegatingServiceProvider

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DelegatingRepositoryContext

    public class DelegatingServiceProvider
extends Object
implements ServiceProvider, IDisposableService
    A service registry that delegates calls to another ServiceProvider if the underlying registry does not have the required service.

    5.0
